    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/4a6cf6ccd8e9369c6fcc545a3e966d7b.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/4a6cf6ccd8e9369c6fcc545a3e966d7b.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/4a6cf6ccd8e9369c6fcc545a3e966d7b.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚特兰蒂斯的建设者》是一款等距视角的城市建设经济战略游戏，其背景是神话中的亚特兰蒂斯大陆。在这个国家，根据传说，它在科学、军事化、经济领域的进步水平超过了其他国家。亚特兰蒂斯是一个位于岛上的国家，分为10个省。这个地方有丰富的农作物、蔬菜、水果、野生动物，还有像钻石这样的宝石，根据传说，几乎到处都能找到，这也是亚特兰蒂斯国家富裕的原因之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/200fc4ebaa84beab1693b372a589ade6.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/200fc4ebaa84beab1693b372a589ade6.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/200fc4ebaa84beab1693b372a589ade6.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中最重要的方面将是通过塑造地区和中心的网格来巧妙地管理城市规划。一个设计良好的城市将大大改善其经济效率，这将进一步转化为赚取的收入。另一方面，错误的决定或忽视城市生活的某些方面甚至会导致整个社区的悲剧性死亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/5aa10455bc3096b7c9bb67d6e4d819ee.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/5aa10455bc3096b7c9bb67d6e4d819ee.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/5aa10455bc3096b7c9bb67d6e4d819ee.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们将不得不照顾到粮食作物和牲畜养殖，以及饮用水的获取，随着发展，甚至是污水管网，人口居住越高，城市的效率和发展就越高。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们将不得不照顾人口的教育，并决定学校的建设及其专业，我们将能够在生活的各个领域教导人们，例如，农业、卫生、建筑、技术、军国主义、医学、政治、商业、哲学以及艺术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们将不得不照顾军队和舰队，亚特兰蒂斯通过其财富成为频繁的攻击目标，保卫岛屿的能力将是城市发展的一个关键方面。发展自己的舰队不仅有助于领土防卫，还能为贸易和军事远征开辟机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/021fe1a3809406e96b710845ea1158a4.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/021fe1a3809406e96b710845ea1158a4.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/021fe1a3809406e96b710845ea1158a4.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >政治家和哲学家的教育将使我们有机会增加与其他国家建立和平关系的机会，这将转化为，稳定发展和高收入。我们还必须注意州内的政治情绪，这将取决于我们管理城市的决定，以及来自其他州或自然灾害的威胁。艺术和娱乐将是我们必须发展的另一个方面，以保持居民的高昂士气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/ed87201e988137db8cb882fd3e1316d5.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/ed87201e988137db8cb882fd3e1316d5.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/ed87201e988137db8cb882fd3e1316d5.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚特兰蒂斯尽管拥有丰富的土地，但却很容易被水淹没，甚至整个沉没。游戏的另一个要素将是扩大城市，使其尽可能少地暴露于沉没之中。为此，我们将不得不学习新技术，并寻找生存之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1772203361\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1772203361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。</p>",
